theorem Topology.P3_iUnion {ι : Sort _} {X : Type _} [TopologicalSpace X] {f : ι → Set X} :
    (∀ i, Topology.P3 (f i)) → Topology.P3 (⋃ i, f i) := by
  intro hP3
  unfold Topology.P3 at *
  intro x hx
  rcases mem_iUnion.1 hx with ⟨i, hxi⟩
  have hInt : x ∈ interior (closure (f i)) := hP3 i hxi
  have hSubsetClosure : closure (f i) ⊆ closure (⋃ j, f j) := by
    apply closure_mono
    intro y hy
    exact mem_iUnion.2 ⟨i, hy⟩
  have hSubset : interior (closure (f i)) ⊆ interior (closure (⋃ j, f j)) :=
    interior_mono hSubsetClosure
  exact hSubset hInt

theorem Topology.P2_empty {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] :
    Topology.P2 (∅ : Set X) := by
  unfold Topology.P2
  intro x hx
  cases hx
